    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The dual-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced for long-term structural integrity. Power is transmitted via a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec suspension geometry, and the exterior retains a deep, high-gloss luster. Mechanically flawless with zero fluid seepage or bushing deflection, this is an investment-grade driver\u2019s machine.",
